action.text:
Looking for proof that age is just a number in business? @rachhwilde launched tbh Skincare at just 24, spotting what major beauty brands were missing: products that were both high-performance AND sustainable.

The brand exploded, but success came with serious growing pains. Imposter syndrome, scaling chaos, and the pressure of running a viral eCommerce company tested everything she thought she knew about entrepreneurship.

@NathanChan from @foundr pulls back the curtain on Rachael's journey, covering:
- Building a cult-favorite brand from scratch
- Her costliest early mistake (plus the lesson that came with it)
- The exact playbook behind products that go viral and convert
- Landing major retail partnerships
- Conquering self-doubt as a young founder
- Making a family business partnership actually work

This conversation hits different if you've ever questioned your own readiness to build something big.

Drop your takeaways in the comments!

Full episode on YouTube ‚Äì search 'Foundr Rachael Wilde'.

Comment "PODCAST" for a DM with our full conversation!

#foundr #entrepreneur #skincare #tbhskincare #businessgrowth #ecommerce #youngentrepreneur #startup #brandbuilding #entrepreneurship #podcast #businesspodcast
